---
const hotmartUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_HOTMART_URL || 'https://pay.hotmart.com/P104306248S';
---

<section class="relative gradient-hero section-padding overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background glow -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[300px] rounded-full bg-purple-heart/20 blur-[100px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="section-intro mb-5">
      BTS ya te dio las palabras
    </p>

    <h2 class="section-title text-white-glow mb-5">
      Este journal te da el espacio.
    </h2>

    <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg text-soft-lilac max-w-lg mx-auto mb-5 leading-relaxed">
      35 canciones. 85+ prompts. Un journal hecho <strong class="text-white-glow">por ARMY, para ARMY</strong>. Tu espacio para escribir lo que siempre quisiste decir.
    </p>

    <!-- Cita BTS — Namjoon -->
    <p class="font-heading italic text-base md:text-lg text-white-glow/80 mb-8 max-w-md mx-auto">
      "Maybe I made a mistake yesterday, but yesterday's me is still me. Today I am who I am with all of my faults and my mistakes."
      <span class="block font-body not-italic text-sm text-soft-lilac/70 mt-2">— Kim Namjoon</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Price anchor -->
    <div class="mb-8">
      <span class="font-body text-lg text-soft-lilac/70 line-through">$24.90</span>
      <span class="font-body text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white-glow ml-3">$9.90</span>
      <p class="font-accent text-lg text-white-glow/80 mt-2">Precio especial de lanzamiento</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main CTA -->
    <a
      href={hotmartUrl}
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="btn-primary-lg"
    >
      Quiero empezar mi journal 💜
    </a>

    <!-- Hotmart trust badge -->
    <div class="mt-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white-glow/15 border border-soft-lilac/30 rounded-full px-5 py-2.5">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-white-glow/95">
          Compra segura con <strong class="text-white-glow">Hotmart</strong> — la plataforma #1 de productos digitales
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="font-body text-xs text-soft-lilac/70">
        Descarga inmediata &middot; PDF digital &middot; 165 páginas &middot; 7 capítulos
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Garantía -->
    <div class="mt-6 bg-white-glow/10 border border-soft-lilac/20 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 max-w-sm mx-auto">
      <p class="font-body text-sm text-white-glow/90">
        <strong>Garantía Hotmart de 15 días.</strong> Si no es lo que esperabas, Hotmart te devuelve tu dinero. Sin preguntas.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Signature -->
    <div class="mt-10">
      <img
        src="/images/firma-purple-heart.png"
        alt="Firma de Purple Heart"
        class="h-10 md:h-12 mx-auto opacity-80"
        loading="lazy"
        onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block'"
      />
      <p class="hidden font-accent text-xl text-white-glow/60">Purple Heart</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
